0:13:55.300,0:14:02.720
there are three habits you must learn.

0:14:02.720,0:14:11.300
I call it "habit" because habit is a gift;

0:14:11.300,0:14:15.040
it's a gift of God.

0:14:15.040,0:14:22.640
There are three habits you must learn.

0:14:22.640,0:14:48.060
