0:15:11.500,0:15:18.100
If you talk to Him, He must talk to you.

0:15:18.100,0:15:29.120
If you talk to Him in Spirit and truth, He must talk to you.

0:15:29.120,0:15:43.500
When you talk to Him and He does not talk to you, it means, you are talking to yourself.

0:15:43.500,0:15:57.940
