0:18:01.640,0:18:09.520
this is the language that we use to gossip,

0:18:09.520,0:18:16.460
the language we use to tell stories,

0:18:16.460,0:18:22.440
the language we use to do business,

0:18:22.440,0:18:31.660
the language we use to play today's politics

0:18:31.660,0:18:45.180
and the language we use to talk to our children: "Leave the place! Don't be silly!"

0:18:45.180,0:19:02.600
Such language cannot be used to talk to God and to talk to someone else about God.

0:19:02.600,0:19:07.820
This is the language we use today.

0:19:07.820,0:19:12.200
That is why God cannot hear us.

0:19:12.200,0:19:17.580
That is why you cannot hear from God.

0:19:17.580,0:19:20.680
Peru Crusade With Prophet T.B. Joshua - Day 1

